parameters: \lsoff"Dress is a very underappreciated aspect of puppet design. You are doing well in acknowledging this, but remember - frills only serve to enhance the body beneath."
\lsoff"Many of my disciples think far too much in theory, putting little into practice. You, however, are tied to the physical and are strengthening your talents. Keep it up..."
\lsoff"Your reading of my works is exhaustive, nearly religious. This is good. Absorb my knowledge and you, too, may one day reach perfection..."
\lsoff"I was skeptical of the possible applications of astrological magics in puppetcraft, but I must admit that you have me intrigued. Continue, and we shall see where this leads."
\lsoff"Soulsmithing and puppetry have traditionally been seen as contradicting forces, but traditions are only good for so much. I commend your work."
\lsoff"This workspace is available. Contact me in my workshop via the password if you have a project you wish to use it for."
\lsoff"Produce results soon, disciple. And remember - another act of stupidity as egregious as your last *will* result in the removal of your sentience."
\lsoff"Your recipes are interesting, yes, but their effects extend only to organic beings. They are useless. Try again and produce results, or you will join the puppet heap..."
